Syiid is a symbol of the resilience of those who are marginalized and forgotten in society, and their tenacity serves as an inspiration to others.

As an NFT, Syiid is a unique and valuable asset. Their representation captures the essence of the struggles that so many individuals face every day, making them a powerful symbol of social justice and empathy.
